features: Made with sturdy and premium quality plastic material, the cars are not only long-lasting but also safe for your kids to handle. This toy is recommended for children aged 18 months or above. Although, it is advised that the adults always keep an eye on their toddlers while they are playing.

This toy car set has 9 different types of bright-coloured vehicles, including an aeroplane, a dump truck, a mixer truck, a taxi, a school bus, a city bus, a transport truck, and a sprinkler. Some of the vehicles have removable parts to increase the fun.
The varied style of this toy set ignites your kid’s imaginary skills, stimulating curiosity and encouraging hand-eye coordination. This set helps your child to promote recognition stability too.

No batteries required, energy saving and environmental protection. All you need to do is just pull the car back and it will move forward. Easy for toddlers to operate. Carrier trailer size : 13.5 * 5.5 inch, small cars size: 2.5 *1.6 inch.
This car toy set is a treat for your kid and their friends. Gift it in birthdays, or any other festive occasion, or just like that, and their smile and joy will say it all.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Let Your Toddler Feel The Thrill With This Toy Car Set. This set is perfect for all the kids to play together and develop social skills. Remember being a kid how excited you used to get after finding out more than one toy inside a gift box! Then you can imagine how great a gift this car toy set can be. The 9 different variation of cars from this set is surely the best thing that can happen to your child. It is easy to operate and safe to handle. So, the next time all the kids gather around, they can easily play together without fighting. This proves that this toy set enhances your kid’s social skills. Additionally, the inertia of the vehicles will teach your kid hand-eye coordination. The 9 different models will cultivate their curiosity to know more while bringing attention to detail. The different shapes and colours of the cars will stimulate their visual development.

RECOGNITION SKILLS: The set will not only educate your kids with vehicle information and colour recognition but also with motor skills and dexterity. It is best for kids between 2-5 years old, allowing them to develop different skills and grow to be smarter. SPECIAL EFFECTS: Push the button above the carrier truck to enjoy lifelike sound effects, enhancing the playtime experience. OPERATION: Pull the vehicles back to get them moving. No need for batteries. The small cars will easily fit into the carrier truck, adding more excitement and imagination to the game. SIZE: The size of the carrier trailer is 13.5 inches x 5.5 inches, and the small ones are of 2.5 inches x 1.6 inches. Thus, they are ideally made for your kids to grip.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for One Year Olds
reviews.reviewText: My son loves this so much! Each piece is crafted with attention to detail and vibrant colors that immediately catch the eye. The variety of vehicles, from a truck with a trailer to an airplane, provides endless fun and encourages imaginative play. They’re the perfect size for little hands, promoting fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination.The durability is impressive; despite the countless drops and rough play, each piece remains intact and safe for my son.This set has become a staple in our playtime, providing not just entertainment but also a learning experience as my boy discovers the different functions of each vehicle. It’s a fantastic investment that fosters creativity, learning, and pure joy. I couldn’t be happier with this purchase and highly recommend it to any parent looking for a high-quality, engaging toy set for their toddler.
